Hyponex Corp is raising 150 mln dlrsthrough an offering of senior subordinated debentures due 1999yielding 11.828 pct, said sole underwriter Drexel BurnhamLambert Inc.    The debentures have an 11-3/4 pct coupon and were priced at99.50, Drexel said.    The issue is non-callable for five years. There were noratings by Moody's Investors Service Inc or Standard and Poor'sCorp at the time of the pricing, Drexel said. Hyponex saidproceeds will be used mainly to finance acquisitions of assetsand businesses. Reuter&#3;